 shares overdraft facilities to individuals and financing services such as term and installment loans overdraft trade finance project finance syndicated loans etc to enterprises in addition the company offers life general and commercial insurance products and services remittance services mandatory provident fund services investment services including investment funds structured deposits bond investments physical gold trading paper gold and foreign exchange margin trading services securities services consisting of stock trading and internetmobile stock trading services debit cards and internet banking services further it engages in the provision of nominee trustee commodities trading services and it application services investment in exchange fund bills insurance brokerage and notes and bonds and property holding and management activities the company has  branches in hong kong and overseas branches in new york los angeles san francisco and london as well as in mainland china shanghai commercial bank limited was founded in  and is headquartered in central hong kong shanghai commercial bank limited is a subsidiary of the shanghai commercial  savings bank ltd detailed description shanghai commercial bank tower queens roadcentral  hong kongfounded in  employees wwwshacombankcomhk key executives for shanghai commercial bank limited mr sekchi kwok fhkib fcib chief executive officer managing director and executive director age  ms lichien weng chief financial controller and executive vice president age  mr chishan cheng alternate chief executive and chief of information technology  operations age  mr waitai law chief of legal  compliance and executive vice president ms chorhing fung chief of human resources and executive vice president compensation as of fiscal year  shanghai commercial bank limited key developments shanghai commercial bank announces consolidated earnings results for the year ended december   provides earnings guidance for the year  apr   shanghai commercia